Repeat: p6, slip next 2 stitches to dpn and hold in back, k2, then k2 from dpn
p6, slip next 2 stitches to dpn and hold in back, k2, then k2 from dpn
k3- tog-b, k3- tog, pass the first of these 2 stitches over the second; p4
End Row: k3-tog-b, k3-tog, pass the first of these 2 stitches over the second; k1

Repeat: (k1, p1) 3 times in the next stitch, making 6 stitches from one; yo, k2 tog-b, k2-tog, yo
End Row: (k1, p1) 3 times in next stitch, k1
